</taxonomicName>
. Left, dorsal view of the skull, with cartilages stained with Alcian Blue and bones with Alizarin Red. Scale bar: 10 mm. Right, landmarks on the skull. Abbreviations: exo, exoccipital; fr, frontal; ma, maxilla; na, nasal; osph, orbitosphenoid; pa, parietal; pfr, prefrontal; pma, premaxilla; pt, pterygoid; q, quadrate; sq, squamosal.
</paragraph>
</caption>
